{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"border-top-left-radius","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/border-top-left-radius","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"概要","title":"概要","isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong><code>border-top-left-radius</code></strong> 用来设置元素左上角的圆角效果。这段圆弧（角）可以是圆或椭圆的一部分。如果其中有一个值为 0，那么将无圆角效果（见<strong><code>border-top-left-radius取值方式</code></strong><code>)。</code></p>\n\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\" id=\"sect1\"><img alt=\"border-radius.png\" class=\"default internal\" src=\"/@api/deki/files/6132/=border-radius.png\" loading=\"lazy\"></div>\n\n<p>盒模型的背景，可以是一张图片或一种颜色，会在边框处被剪裁，更甚至可以是一个圆；剪切的额外定位通过另一个 CSS 属性\"background-clip\"来定义。</p>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect2\">在 border-top-left-radius 属性值之后，如果作用的元素上没有设置“border-radius”属性，那么这个属性值就会通过<a href=\"/en/CSS/Shorthand_properties\" title=\"en/CSS/Shorthand_properties\">简写属性</a>重新设置成它的初始值。</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"语法","title":"语法","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush:css notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token comment\">/* the corner is a circle */</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">/* border-top-left-radius: radius */</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">border-top-left-radius</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 3px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">/* the corner is an ellipsis */</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">/* border-top-left-radius: horizontal vertical */</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">border-top-left-radius</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 0.5em 1em<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token property\">border-top-left-radius</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> inherit<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<div style=\"font-size: 0.9em;\" id=\"sect3\">\n<h5 id=\"属性值：\">属性值：</h5>\n\n<dl style=\"padding-left: 6em;\">\n <dt id=\"radius\"><em>radius</em></dt>\n <dd>可以是 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/length\" title=\"此页面仍未被本地化, 期待您的翻译!\"><code>&lt;length&gt;</code></a> 或者 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/percentage\" title=\"此页面仍未被本地化, 期待您的翻译!\"><code>&lt;percentage&gt;</code></a>，表示左上角边框的圆角半径。</dd>\n <dt id=\"horizontal\"><em>horizontal</em></dt>\n <dd>可以是 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/length\" title=\"此页面仍未被本地化, 期待您的翻译!\"><code>&lt;length&gt;</code></a> 或者 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/percentage\" title=\"此页面仍未被本地化, 期待您的翻译!\"><code>&lt;percentage&gt;</code></a>，表示椭圆的水平半长轴在被用作边框左上角的半径。</dd>\n <dt id=\"vertical\"><em>vertical</em></dt>\n <dd>可以是 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/length\" title=\"此页面仍未被本地化, 期待您的翻译!\"><code>&lt;length&gt;</code></a> 或者 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/percentage\" title=\"此页面仍未被本地化, 期待您的翻译!\"><code>&lt;percentage&gt;</code></a>，表示椭圆的垂直半长轴在被用作边框左上角的半径。</dd>\n</dl>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"取值","title":"取值","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"length\"><code>&lt;length&gt;</code></dt>\n <dd><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/length\" title=\"此页面仍未被本地化, 期待您的翻译!\"><code>&lt;length&gt;</code></a> 定义圆形半径或椭圆的半长轴，半短轴。不能用负值。</dd>\n <dt id=\"percentage\"><code>&lt;percentage&gt;</code></dt>\n <dd>使用百分数定义圆形半径或椭圆的半长轴，半短轴。水平半轴相对于盒模型的宽度；垂直半轴相对于盒模型的高度。不能用负值。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"formal_syntax","title":"Formal syntax","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"notranslate\"><a href=\"#length-percentage\">&lt;length-percentage&gt;</a><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#curly_braces\" title=\"Curly braces: encloses two integers defining the minimal and maximal numbers of occurrences of the entity\">{</a>1,2<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#curly_braces\" title=\"Curly braces: encloses two integers defining the minimal and maximal numbers of occurrences of the entity\">}</a><p style=\"font-family:Open Sans,Arial,sans-serif; margin: 10px 0 0 0;\">where <br><code style=\"font-family:Consolas,Monaco,&quot;Andale Mono&quot;,monospace;\"><span id=\"length-percentage\">&lt;length-percentage&gt;</span> = <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/length\" title=\"Possible values: a number followed by'em', 'ex', 'ch', 'rem', 'px', 'cm', 'mm', 'in', 'vh', 'vw', 'vmin', 'vmax', 'pt', 'pc' or 'px', like 3px, 1.5cm, -0.5em or 0\">&lt;length&gt;</a> <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#single_bar\" title=\"Single bar: exactly one of the entities must be present\">|</a> <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/percentage\" title=\"\">&lt;percentage&gt;</a></code></p></pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"示例","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th>实例</th>\n   <th>代码</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td style=\"padding: 1.5em;\">\n    <div id=\"circle-arc\" style=\"background-color: lightgreen; border: solid 1px black; border-top-left-radius: 40px 40px; width: 100px; height: 100px;\">&nbsp;</div>\n   </td>\n   <td>椭圆的弧被用作左上角边框\n    <div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush:css notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token selector\">div</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">border-top-left-radius</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 40px 40px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n   </td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td style=\"padding: 1.5em;\">\n    <div id=\"ellipse-arc\" style=\"background-color: lightgreen; border: solid 1px black; border-top-left-radius: 40px 20px; width: 100px; height: 100px;\">&nbsp;</div>\n   </td>\n   <td>椭圆的弧被用作左上角边框\n    <div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush:css notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token selector\">div</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">border-top-left-radius</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 40px 20px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n   </td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td style=\"padding: 1.5em;\">\n    <div id=\"square-box-circle-arc\" style=\"background-color: lightgreen; border: solid 1px black; border-top-left-radius: 40%; width: 100px; height: 100px;\">&nbsp;</div>\n   </td>\n   <td>盒子是方形的，圆弧被用作左上角边框\n    <div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: css notranslate\"><code>div\n  <span class=\"token property\">border-top-left-radius</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 40%<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n   </td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td style=\"padding: 1.5em;\">\n    <div id=\"not-square-ellipse-arc\" style=\"background-color: lightgreen; border: solid 1px black; border-top-left-radius: 40%; width: 100px; height: 200px;\">&nbsp;</div>\n   </td>\n   <td>盒子不是方形的，椭圆的弧被用作左上角边框\n    <div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: css notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token selector\">div</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">border-top-left-radius</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 40%<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n   </td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td style=\"padding: 1.5em;\">\n    <div id=\"clipped-border\" style=\"background-color: rgb(250,20,70); background-clip: content-box; border: double 3px black; border-top-left-radius: 40%; width: 100px; height: 100px;\">&nbsp;</div>\n   </td>\n   <td>背景色在左上角被剪切\n    <div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: css notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token selector\">div</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">border-top-left-radius</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>40%<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">border-style</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> black 3px double<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background-color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">rgb</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>250<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>20<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>70<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background-clip</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> content-box<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n   </td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"规范","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-backgrounds/#the-border-radius","title":"CSS Backgrounds and Borders Module Level 4"}],"query":"css.properties.border-top-left-radius"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"css.properties.border-top-left-radius","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/border-top-left-radius/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"另请参阅","title":"另请参阅","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li>border-radius 相关 CSS 属性：<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/border-radius\"><code>border-radius</code></a>, 其他边角属性： <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/border-top-right-radius\"><code>border-top-right-radius</code></a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/border-bottom-right-radius\"><code>border-bottom-right-radius</code></a>, and <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/border-bottom-left-radius\"><code>border-bottom-left-radius</code></a>.</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"概要","id":"概要"},{"text":"语法","id":"语法"},{"text":"示例","id":"示例"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"},{"text":"另请参阅","id":"另请参阅"}],"summary":"border-top-left-radius 用来设置元素左上角的圆角效果。这段圆弧（角）可以是圆或椭圆的一部分。如果其中有一个值为 0，那么将无圆角效果（见border-top-left-radius取值方式)。","popularity":0.0004,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"border-top-left-radius","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"border-top-left-radius","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"border-top-left-radius","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"border-top-left-radius","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"border-top-left-radius","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"-moz-border-radius-topleft","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/css/border-top-left-radius","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/css/border-top-left-radius/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS","title":"CSS（层叠样式表）"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/border-top-left-radius","title":"border-top-left-radius"}],"pageTitle":"border-top-left-radius - CSS（层叠样式表） | MDN","noIndexing":false}}